- dnsrecon (DNS reconnaissance)
- dig (DNS lookup)
- whois (domain info)
- host (DNS utility)
- theharvester (data harvesting)

Password Testing:
- hydra (login cracker)
- john (password cracker)
- hashcat (hash cracking)
- crunch (wordlist generator)

System Enumeration:
- enum4linux (SMB enumeration)
- nbtscan (NetBIOS scanner)
- onesixtyone (SNMP scanner)

